    tldr: 'Real-time break-even analysis uses PoS transaction data to calculate how much gross profit you have generated today relative to your daily fixed costs. By mid-afternoon, you know whether the day is tracking toward profitability or loss, giving you hours to adjust staffing, promotions, or operations before the day ends.',
